Catalano.Math.Distances

Class Distance

  • java.lang.Object
    • Catalano.Math.Distances.Distance

  • public final class Distance
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines a set of extension methods defining distance measures. References: http://www.ajmaa.org/RGMIA/papers/v7n4/Gsdmi_RGMIA.pdf http://arabic-icr.googlecode.com/git/Papers/Comprehensive%20Survey%20on%20Distance-Similarity.pdf
